<subSubSection pageId="22" pageNumber="23" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="22.[151,1436,1374,1437]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
This group is composed by seven genera and 29 species, distributed in the Neotropical and Ethiopic regions. Here we present the first record of the group for the 
<collectingRegion box="[675,817,1410,1436]" country="Brazil" name="Parana" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Paraná State</collectingRegion>
, including two genera and five species.
</paragraph>
